subsingleton_of_is_terminal:
-- The factor map is a ⊗ b ↦ f(a) * g(b).
theorem subsingleton_of_is_terminal {X : CommRing} (hX : IsTerminal X) : subsingleton X :=
  (hX.unique_up_to_iso punit_is_terminal).CommRing_iso_to_ring_equiv.to_equiv.subsingleton_congr.mpr
    (show subsingleton PUnit by infer_instance)
#align subsingleton_of_is_terminal subsingleton_of_is_terminal
pushout_cocone_inr:
@[simp]
theorem pushout_cocone_inr :
    (pushout_cocone f g).inr = by
      letI := f.to_algebra
      letI := g.to_algebra
      exact algebra.tensor_product.include_right.to_ring_hom :=
  rfl
#align pushout_cocone_inr pushout_cocone_inr
